Key Features & Functionalities
Energy-Efficient Tracking: Ultra-low power draw for long battery life
Proximity Monitoring: Real-time distance-based alerts
Geo-Zoning: Define zones where BLE readers detect entry/exit
Activity Monitoring: Basic motion tracking and inactivity alerts
Offline Data Storage: Store data locally during signal loss, auto-upload when reconnected
Multi-User Access: Share device visibility with staff or veterinary teams